{
  "texts": [
    "The long audio file is chunked into smaller segments with a small overlap between adjacent segments.",
    "The model is run over each chunk, and the inferred text is joined at the strides by finding the longest common sequence between overlaps.",
    "Once we have generated the N-best list, we select the top 5 candidates and utilize an LLM to produce the final hypothesis as shown in Figure 1.",
    "In this step, we can adapt the LLM to the task using either few-shot prompting or LoRA fine-tuning techniques.",
    "We choose to fine-tune the LLM with adapters based on the findings from (Chen et al., 2024)."
  ]
}